name: Mark Evans - pass the time // think of you

attributes.trait_type: pass the time // think of you

metadata.description:
hey :) this is my first solo release on here. I wrote this song in mid 2020 and have been waiting for the right time to share it and i think that time is now. I haven't released it anywhere so it will be exclusive here. when i wrote the song i had just broken my wrist and it was peak lockdown and i was just on a tear of writing songs and trying to escape the reality of what life was. i hope it feels as special to you as it does to me <3 

mark
metadata.name: pass the time // think of you #1
